<h2>Password Reset</h2>
<p><strong>Hello,</strong></p>
<p>You can reset your password within the next 15 minutes by clicking the button below:</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <%= link_to "Reset Password", edit_password_url(@user.password_reset_token), class: "btn" %>
</div>

<p>If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
<p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; font-family: monospace; background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cccccc;"><%= edit_password_url(@user.password_reset_token) %></p>